      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/File:Genzgen-isa-140809-koeln-ludwigmuseum.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Genzgen-isa-140809-koeln-ludwigmuseum.jpg/250px-Genzgen-isa-140809-koeln-ludwigmuseum.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Genzgen-isa-140809-koeln-ludwigmuseum.jpg/330px-Genzgen-isa-140809-koeln-ludwigmuseum.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Genzgen-isa-140809-koeln-ludwigmuseum.jpg/500px-Genzgen-isa-140809-koeln-ludwigmuseum.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Genzgen-isa-140809-koeln-ludwigmuseum.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Isa Genzken</div></div></div> \n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isa_Genzken\">Isa Genzken</a>,<br />\na German sculptor and artist, using a wide variety of materials, including <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Concrete\">concrete</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plaster\">plaster</a>, wood and textile. She also works with photography, video, film and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Collage\">collage</a>.\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301064348\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.058 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.603 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00